title: Calum Scott, Aberg in top-10 at Thunderbird Collegiate - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Calum Scott, Aberg in top-10 at Thunderbird Collegiate - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Texas Tech freshman Calum Scott and junior Ludvig Aberg are in the top-10 at the Thunderbird Collegiate after 36 holes on Friday to help the No. 7 Red Raiders remain in contention going into the final round on Saturday at the Papago Golf Course.
